---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import ProjectGallery from "../../components/ProjectGallery.astro";

const projectImages = [
  {
    src: "/projects/intern-engagement-1.png",
    alt: "Team building and collaboration activities"
  },
  {
    src: "/projects/intern-engagement-2.png",
    alt: "Community engagement initiatives"
  },
  {
    src: "/projects/intern-engagement-3.jpeg",
    alt: "Team engagement activity"
  },
  {
    src: "/projects/intern-engagement-4.jpeg",
    alt: "Fundraising event"
  },
  {
    src: "/projects/intern-engagement-5.png",
    alt: "Project outcomes and metrics"
  }
];
---

<BaseLayout title="Intern Engagement Leadership" sideBarActiveItemID="projects">
  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">üåç Intern Engagement Leadership at Emera</div>
    <div class="py-2">
      <span class="badge badge-primary mr-2">Leadership</span>
      <span class="badge badge-outline">Event Management</span>
      <span class="badge badge-outline">Community Building</span>
      <span class="badge badge-outline">Brand Representation</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="prose max-w-none">
    <ProjectGallery images={projectImages} />
    
    <h2>Project Overview</h2>
    <p>
      While interning at Emera, I went beyond my core responsibilities and volunteered to lead the co-op student committee. 
      This presented an opportunity to influence culture and build connections across departments, addressing a noticeable lack of intern engagement.
    </p>

    <h2>Key Initiatives</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-4">
      <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-lg">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="card-title">Fundraising Campaign</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Organized campaign for local food bank</li>
            <li>Managed logistics and marketing</li>
            <li>Coordinated across departments</li>
            <li>Successfully raised $1,200</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-lg">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="card-title">Volunteer Clean-up Event</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Planned and executed community event</li>
            <li>Handled event logistics</li>
            <li>Ensured strong participation</li>
            <li>Enhanced company visibility</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2>University Hiring Fair Representation</h2>
    <p>
      Selected to represent Emera at a university hiring fair, where I:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Collaborated with HR to design effective booth messaging</li>
      <li>Shared personal intern experiences to attract candidates</li>
      <li>Engaged with potential applicants</li>
      <li>Promoted company culture and opportunities</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Results & Impact</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 my-4">
      <div class="stats shadow">
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-title">Funds Raised</div>
          <div class="stat-value text-primary">$1,200</div>
          <div class="stat-desc">For local food bank</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="stats shadow">
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-title">Intern Participation</div>
          <div class="stat-value text-secondary">+60%</div>
          <div class="stat-desc">Increase in engagement</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="stats shadow">
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-title">Hiring Fair</div>
          <div class="stat-value">20+</div>
          <div class="stat-desc">Interested applicants</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Key Learnings</h2>
    <p>
      This experience reinforced my belief that strong internal communities and external brand presence are both critical to organizational success. 
      Key takeaways include:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Leadership doesn't require a title, just initiative</li>
      <li>The power of community-building in corporate culture</li>
      <li>Importance of authentic brand representation</li>
      <li>Value of cross-departmental collaboration</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-8">
    <a href="/projects" class="btn btn-outline">‚Üê Back to Projects</a>
  </div>
</BaseLayout> 